OL,3,CGirl, 14, told teacher 'I'm going to
OL,4,Ckill you' before school stabbing
OL,6,FA 14-year-old girl told police "that's
OL,7,Fone way to be a celebrity" after she
OL,8,Fstabbed two teachers and another
OL,9,Fteenager at a school in Wales, a court
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FSwansea Crown Court was played CCTV
OL,13,Ffootage of the girl attacking the two
OL,14,Fteachers at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman, also
OL,15,Fknown as Amman Valley School, in
OL,16,FAmmanford, Carmarthenshire, and then
OL,17,Fmoving on to stab another girl before
OL,18,Fshe was disarmed by staff.
OL,20,FThe 14-year-old defendant cannot be
OL,21,Fnamed for legal reasons due to her age.
