OL,6,FThe jury has been told that the
OL,7,Fdefendant has admitted attacking all
OL,8,Fthree people at the school.
OL,10,FShe has pleaded guilty to three counts
OL,11,Fof wounding with intent and one of
OL,12,Fpossessing a bladed article article on
OL,13,Fschool premises.
OL,15,FThe girl denies three counts of
OL,16,Fattempted murder in relation to the
OL,17,Fincident on April 24, when she was 13.
