OL,3,CGirl, 14, told teacher 'I'm going to
OL,4,Ckill you' before school stabbing
OL,6,FOpening the girl's trial on Monday, 30
OL,7,FSeptember, prosecutor William Hughes
OL,8,FKC said that she told police officers
OL,9,Fafter she was arrested: "I'm pretty
OL,10,Fsure this is going to be on the news.
OL,12,F"So more eyes will be looking at me.
OL,13,FThat's one way to be a celebrity."
OL,15,FBut she also asked "are they dead" and
OL,16,Fadded: "How am I going to face my
OL,17,Ffamily after what I've done?"
