OL,6,FThe court heard that the girl
OL,7,Fdescribed the attack on the teenager
OL,8,Fto the officers, saying: "I stabbed
OL,9,Fher, oopsies".
OL,11,FMr Hughes said the girl confronted
OL,12,Fassistant head Fiona Elias in the
OL,13,Fschool yard, telling her: "I'm going
OL,14,Fto kill you, I'm going to f*****g kill
OL,15,Fyou", before launching her attack with
OL,16,Fa multi-tool that her father used for
OL,17,Ffishing.
OL,19,FThe video showed how Mrs Elias was
OL,20,Fwith fellow teacher Liz Hopkin, who
OL,21,Fimmediately intervened.
