OL,6,FMr Hughes said Ms Hopkin ended up with
OL,7,Fthe more serious injuries, to her
OL,8,Fback, neck, legs and arms, and had to
OL,9,Fbe airlifted for treatment.
OL,11,FHe said the teachers later said the
OL,12,Fgirl had "lost it".
OL,14,FThe footage played in court showed how
OL,15,Fa number of teachers arrived quickly
OL,16,Fand talked to the girl, trying to calm
OL,17,Fher down in "a kind of stand off",
OL,18,Fwith the staff later saying she had a
OL,19,F"vacant look on her face".
